# Image Assets Directory

Place your custom stock photos here. See README below for required images.

## Folder Structure
- hero/ - Main hero images
- services/ - Service-specific images  
- facility/ - Facility and equipment photos
- blog/ - Blog/insights featured images

## Recommended Specs
- Format: JPG or WebP
- Hero images: 1600x1200px minimum
- Service images: 800x1000px minimum
- Aspect ratios maintained by Astro Image component
